( sports ) canoe ( short for Canadian canoe , as opposed to kayak )

definitions.definition: ( informal ) The English language (spoken or written) as used in Canada; Canadian English .

definitions.definition: The Canadian River , a river in New Mexico, the Texas Panhandle , and Oklahoma in the United States, which is a tributary of the Arkansas River.
A town in Pittsburg County , Oklahoma .
A city , the county seat of Hemphill County , Texas , situated on the Canadian River.
